Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:12.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,turned to rubber after \Nhe ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Usopp knocked Sugar out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and freed the toys who had been forced to labor as slaves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Doflamingo confined everybody in the country in the Birdcage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's bring an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's started...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Birdcage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo is going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...kill everyone on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The 500 Million Berry Man!\NTarget: Usoland!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's as steady as rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody! Stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody's gonna come to help.\NNobody can get out of this Birdcage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make contact with\Nanyone out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all going to die\Nand no one out there will know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Your neighbors who are running wild...\N--Don't! Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...will keep harming others randomly.\N--Somebody, please stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'm gonna kill my own kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't matter if it's their family or close friends
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nor citizens who they swore to protect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't control my body!\NSomebody, please! Stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me! Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you run or hide,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there is no safe place in the cage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The terror of the Birdcage will go on for days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter of which happens sooner.\NYou all die or you finish the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Doflamingo!\NYou can't anticipate his next move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!\NThe factory went up and is gone now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But this is definitely a good chance for us!\N--We can get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We finally can get out from underground!\N--Thank you, God Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin'emon!\NI'm glad that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-An iron breast-band?!\NThis is quite a foreign culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Robin-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, let me be your slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That guy's nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Sniper King-{\i1}senpai{\i0}'s,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwho is known for shooting out the flag on the Tower of Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him. His name is Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Robin-{\i1}senpai{\i0} was moved by\Nthe action of her pirate group...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that turned the world against them\Nin order to save one of their friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes them\Nthe Enies Lobby Shoot-out Duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you excited for?! You geek!\NShut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my arm broken by this fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I hand them over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NAlthough they're little, they're quite good warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Topknot-land!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found them passed out\Nin a hallway at the Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they laid their lives on the line\Nfor the commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cub-{\i1}san{\i0}! Rampo! I'm proud of you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, stop me!\NMy body's out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly like the incident\Non that night 10 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that night,\NKing Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0} was... the King Riku Army was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...manipulated by...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...manipulated by Doflamingo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scream! Hate! Suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are innocent victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it... Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You either come to kill me or\Nside with us Don Quixote Family{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and punish the 12 fools who rebel against me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you make the wrong decision,\Nthe game will not end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll pay 100 million berries for each star rating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 million berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These are the criminals in Dressrosa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First, the One-stars...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:22.72,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,REBECCA\NA CONVICT GLADIATOR OF THE CORRIDA COLOSSEUM\N(KING RIKU'S GRANDDAUGHTER)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:30.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,NICO ROBIN - A PIRATE OF THE STRAW HATS\N"DEMON CHILD"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:38.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,FOXFIRE KIN'EMON \N- A SAMURAI FROM THE WANO KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:46.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,VIOLA - THE FORMER PRINCESS OF DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:53.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,CYBORG FRANKY - A PIRATE OF THE STRAW HATS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next, the Two-stars...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:06.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,KYROS - THE FORMER ARMY COMMANDER OF DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:14.24,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,PIRATE HUNTER ZORO\N - A PIRATE OF THE STRAW HATS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Army Commander Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about him, the invincible gladiator!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are pirates, too! It's the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know the executive of the Family, Violet, was Princess Viola!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as for key figures of each group,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I give them three stars!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:45.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,SABO - THE CHIEF OF STAFF OF THE REVOLUTIONARY ARMY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:53.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,STRAW HAT LUFFY - A PIRATE\NTHE CAPTAIN OF THE STRAW HATS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:12:01.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,TRAFALGAR LAW - THE CAPTAIN OF "THE HEART PIRATES"\NTHE WARLORD(TENTATIVE), "SURGEON OF DEATH"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:08.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,RIKU DOLDO III - THE FORMER KING OF DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,300 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law and Straw Hat...\NTheir pirate alliance has just startled the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}... He was alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a big gun from the Revolutionary Army!\NHe's the Chief of Staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They knew about you already!\N--I'm a target, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What a relief.\NThey haven't found out about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, there is the man who\Npissed me off the most today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all his fault that you people have to\Nplay such a bloody game!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who kills him will get...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...500 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:11.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"GOD" USOPP - A PIRATE OF THE STRAW HATS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to work for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F... F... Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Oh no, Usoland is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Five-star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two One-stars\Nand one Three-star there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo-{\i1}kun{\i0}, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go above ground! Everybody, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Usopp! I'm sorry but I need to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Five-star! 500 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They were worshiping me\Nuntil a few minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Please run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go look for Kanjuro so excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The One-star samurai! 100 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Little Person told me\Nthere's a junkyard down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really there, Kanjuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--100 million berries is mine!\N--Okay, let's just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fell! The samurai fell down into the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have no time to wonder what to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People are falling and\Ntowns are burning moment by moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Either you kill me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or kill the 12 criminals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now the game is on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just found out that\NKing Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0} was innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we citizens all act together,\Nmaybe we can take down Doflamingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to kill Doflamingo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to fight the 2000 soldiers of the Doflamingo Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to do then?\NEven King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0} is in the 12 criminal list!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we gonna do wrong by the innocent king again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we don't have to kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just take them into custody!\NJust 12 of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice! Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the 12 criminals is\Nknocked out over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Cyborg Franky go?\NHe was down on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back on my feet\Nwith backup cola for destroying the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There's one of the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the ex-toys who were saved by Usopp, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing personal!\NOne-star, 100 million berries, Cyborg Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 million is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you guys be blinded by money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can bring me down, try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly big talkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the criminals is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch him, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about us and just shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, guys!\NI have no business with you town people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made up our mind!\NWe've got to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end if I fight them one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This would do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp did his part so it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna break the factory into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, the factory went up on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Pica.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring... Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trebol!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Doffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Diamante, I didn't know you are there, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy, about Sugar...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both of you, come back to the Palace!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll talk later. Okay?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop following us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! To the ground above!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring... Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Zoro?\N--{\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where are you now?\N--{\i1}Robin?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with Luffy and the others.\NWe're on, what they call, the King's Plateau.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting messy, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see it?!\NMingo's such a jerk, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Usopp's bit was hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did you say, Luffy?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rebecca was also on the list.\NI wonder if she's alright.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here! Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's good that you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soldier is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the soldier go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}?! He turned back to a human, too, didn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tell me, Lucy, what kind of a man is he?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a man?!\NWhat are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That one-legged soldier was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...your father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the old man the statue is of!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I couldn't protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I couldn't protect your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna protect you to the end, with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the day you are filled with happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will always be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna save you now, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soldier-san is a brave man{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He will always be by your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Birthday, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me teach you how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need since I have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna teach you how to not get hurt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans' instincts are much better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in your human power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how long my body's gonna last!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm happy for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soldier guy has gone somewhere now\Nbut listen to me, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't cry yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.75,0:22:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let the soldier die!\NYou have to be safe, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel bad that I couldn't let you have\Nthe Flare-Flare Fruit that you wanted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll kick Doflamingo's ass for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So stay with my friends!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna bring an end to\Nthis stupid game in no time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:22:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So survive! Okay?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:22:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Along with Law and Zoro, Luffy is on the move!{\i0}
